{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HIDInputReportEvent.device","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDInputReportEvent/device","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebHID_API\">WebHID API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HID\"><code>HID</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice\"><code>HIDDevice</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDInputReportEvent\"><code>HIDInputReportEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDConnectionEvent\"><code>HIDConnectionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/hid\"><code>Navigator.hid</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">secure contexts</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>device</code></strong> property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDInputReportEvent\"><code>HIDInputReportEvent</code></a> interface returns the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice\"><code>HIDDevice</code></a> instance that represents the HID interface that sent the input report.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>An <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice\"><code>HIDDevice</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In the following example <code>device</code> is a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice\"><code>HIDDevice</code></a> instance, representing the device sending the report. The <code>productName</code> of this device is logged to the console.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>device<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"inputreport\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> device<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> reportId <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>device<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>productName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://wicg.github.io/webhid/#dom-hidinputreportevent-device","title":"WebHID API"}],"query":"api.HIDInputReportEvent.device"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.HIDInputReportEvent.device","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDInputReportEvent/device/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The device property of the HIDInputReportEvent interface returns the HIDDevice instance that represents the HID interface that sent the input report.","popularity":0,"modified":"2021-09-29T19:20:39.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/hidinputreportevent/device","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/hidinputreportevent/device/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/62601de976ad0e808a4c4a62d0edea7eea95cf34","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDInputReportEvent","title":"HIDInputReportEvent"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDInputReportEvent/device","title":"HIDInputReportEvent.device"}],"pageTitle":"HIDInputReportEvent.device - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}